<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><detail><ingredient><qt num="3人份"><food>紐約客牛排</food></qt><qt num="看肉的份量"><food>薄鹽醬油</food></qt><qt num="少許"><food>醬油膏</food></qt><qt num="少許"><food>蜂蜜</food></qt><qt num="個人喜好"><food>蒜頭</food></qt><qt num="少許"><food>玫瑰鹽</food></qt><qt num="少許"><food>香油</food></qt><qt num="少許"><food>薑</food></qt></ingredient><step><img src="uploaded/pics/1-2-20190502-105307.png"><p>牛排切成約1公份的大小，熟成比較快，肉不易老，較多汁。</p></img><img src="uploaded/pics/2-2-20190502-105307.png"><p>前一天先醃肉，較入味！</p></img><img src="uploaded/pics/3-2-20190502-105307.png"><p>薑少許，磨成泥。跟肉事先醃製。</p></img><img src="uploaded/pics/4-2-20190502-105307.png"><p>先是小火煸蒜頭到焦黃，再放入肉類，不需煮到全熟，以免肉太老、太硬！</p></img><img src="uploaded/pics/5-1-20190504-092914.png"><p>測試</p></img></step></detail>